description:
The Head Mistress of the Sanemori family. She holds an important position among the people of Tenmo. Momoe seems to know the truth about many things - Tenmo, http://anidb.net/ch39364 [Nayuta], even http://anidb.net/ch39362 [Muryou] - so it`s no surprise that when important events take place, Momoe is there to guide the way with her wisdom.
Source: shingu.rightstuf.com
name: Sanemori Momoe
